    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，FSM放在Scheduler内部。数据流从DESC描述符模块开始，它负责从HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault获取元数据。然后DESC通过FETCH触发实际的PatientRecords读取。",
